text: Sudjati (13 March 1954 - 8 December 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was born in Semarang, Indonesia. He was Regent of the Bulungan Regency from 2016 until his death. Sudjati died on 8 December 2020 in Tanjung Selor, Indonesia from COVID-19 at the age of 66.Bupati Bulungan meninggal dunia setelah dikonfirmasi tertular COVID-19 ==References== Category:1954 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Indonesia Category:Indonesian politicians
